{"tid":155550,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"AI新時代 未來職業要思考〈蕭若元：最新蕭析〉","createTime":"2017-03-14T06:32:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-14T07:58:51.000Z","uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e4ef6e05006e5fa42eb95241e62c039619142329","tid":155550,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T06:32:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GADKANdmRqM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DGADKANdmRqM&d=8Se%2B9W40ah4Gl3auq3G%2Bum6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=36638237\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GADKANdmRqM</a><br />\n<br />\n蕭若元:我那天講那些機械人的問題，我還有一些東西想補充。這些機械人中，我最喜歡的是Honda的Asimo，它的行動真的很流暢。這已經研究了三十年，由1985年研究至今，一路逐步改進。<br />\n<br />\n原來港大那機械人是一隻Atlas，買了一隻Atlas。這是世上其中一隻最有名的機械人。機械人研究主要解決的是它的行動問題，包括如何雙腳走路、如何動手、如何感知外界環境。但當中還需要一個程序教它如何工作。那比賽鬥的是程序。要機械人做8件事，像下車、拿東西，救急等﹐要求機械人做齊8件事事，最快做完者得勝。Atlas是會走路的，但港大那個程序寫得不好，結果走了幾步便跌倒。<br />\n<br />\n有些人話這些機械人仍然很愚蠢，過幾十年都未可是幫人做家務。但他可能不知道機械人有多聰明，不是光看機械人公司做研究。那方面是人工智能的問題。機械人公司解決的是我剛才所講的問題，像怎樣控制力度拿一隻杯，而不會握碎那隻杯。他們是解決這些問題，而不是機械人有多聰明的問題。<br />\n世界上有另一批公司研究機械人的智能。其實因為人工智能不一定只用在機械人身上，電腦也會用上人工智能。所以那是另外的公司做的事。像自動駕駛的人工智能，不是機械人，而是設在車裏。基本的人工智能已經存在，但未能和機械人整合。現在GOOGLE買了那間Boston Dynamics公司。Boston Dynamics做了那隻Cheetah，它很厲害有障礙會懂得跳過的。在世界最頂尖機械人中，那個PETMAN都是來自Boston Dynamics。GOOGLE再買一些人工智能公司再加上GOOGLE本身的科技力量來整合。我相信十年會有驚人的成就。日本的孫正義也投資數以千億來開發這方面技術。"},{"pid":"e6c9f9fabf3b4208a6d1540ae0bccecad0a4d201","tid":155550,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T06:33:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8SDcgcVEa3c\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D8SDcgcVEa3c&d=8Se%2B9W40ah4Gl3auq3G%2Bum6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=87c90eee\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8SDcgcVEa3c</a>"},{"pid":"3551087dfade1e9a0e29d87bd73fa0380f60f1a4","tid":155550,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T06:33:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=77UW3LoTcgg&amp;t=21s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D77UW3LoTcgg%26t%3D21s&d=8Se%2B9W40ah4Gl3auq3G%2Bum6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=4674e692\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=77UW3LoTcgg&amp;t=21s</a>"},{"pid":"1fb39306b0b366876288b2aa74ba38a6c8ce9fa7","tid":155550,"uid":18516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T06:35:11.000Z","msg":"電腦大爆炸 指日可待<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07a82a02dc92eb1eb52492fa0e45295a0ce50360","tid":155550,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T06:35:33.000Z","msg":"GOOGLE再買一些人工智能公司再加上GOOGLE本身的科技力量來整合。我相信十年會有驚人的成就。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n睇來呢個領域google會輸 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22cf63a3b92453a3000f66c76685c468eee996e4","tid":155550,"uid":57705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T06:57:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7ca7aae321483c02757bfa59beaef86928cd19ff","tid":155550,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T07:34:09.000Z","msg":"honda very dead<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b19cede7c2c9e5a4865eb18790dd04fe1e67fbe3","tid":155550,"uid":25424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T07:56:38.000Z","msg":"Google 仆街了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38590209b356d02de92887758310b0d7be3e3660","tid":155550,"uid":11001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T07:57:22.000Z","msg":"AI玩撚完 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"284dec74b317b23e1fa9c4030101f2247f9fa7db","tid":155550,"uid":15622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T07:58:51.000Z","msg":"成個AI工業molamola<img src=